description: Betty Danger’s Country Club (for the 99%) is sharing its treacherously delectable “Mexampton” cuisine with the streets of the Twin Cities. Taking the finest flavors of Mexico, Minnesota, and The Hamptons, their menu is prepped to tailor to the preppiest of tastes. A few of the items include…Parker Chicken Tacos with tender beer-braised chicken, aged cheddar & fontina, and cilantro cream in crispy corn tortillasChilled Shrimp Tacos with plump poached shrimp, fresh artisan lettuce, jalapeno mayo, pickled red onions & pickled jalapenos, and queso fresco in a flour tortillaFried Plantains with Salsa Verde- so very perfectly sweet and savory, with a kickFor all this and more, be sure to live in delicious luxury by visiting Betty Danger’s Food Truck soon.
name: Betty Danger's Food Truck
